*** Settings ***
Library    BuiltIn

*** Keywords ***
Add Two Numbers Globally
    [Arguments]    ${a}    ${b}
    ${result}=    Evaluate    ${a} + ${b}
    [Return]    ${result}


*** Settings ***
Resource    ../Resources/math_keywords.robot

*** Test Cases ***
Add Two Numbers Using Global Keyword
    ${sum}=    Add Two Numbers Globally    10    20
    Log To Console    Global Sum = ${sum}

Add Two Numbers Using Local Keyword
    ${sum}=    Add Two Numbers Locally    5    7
    Log To Console    Local Sum = ${sum}

*** Keywords ***
Add Two Numbers Locally
    [Arguments]    ${x}    ${y}
    ${result}=    Evaluate    ${x} + ${y}
    [Return]    ${result}
